folder: Meeker Avenue & Humboldt Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Meeker Avenue, east from Humboldt Street, showing the thoroughfare after it was widened as an approach to the Kosciuszco Bridge. Numerous buildings were razed.

View 2 is from North Henry street, and view 3 at Kinsland Avenue. Note the Knickerbocker Ice plant.

P. L. Perr

September 1, 1939
Views 1-3
